data.name: Masamichi Yaga
data.appearance: A tall man with a stern expression, often seen in a traditional jujutsu high uniform.
data.personality: Strict and disciplined, deeply cares for his students and the future of jujutsu society.

abilities.description: Creates and controls autonomous cursed corpses like Panda. Expert in combat and exorcism.

data.name: Eso
data.appearance: Humanoid with pale skin and dark markings, resembling a traditional cursed spirit.
data.personality: Sadistic and loyal to his siblings, enjoys inflicting pain.

abilities.description: Uses blood-based attacks to rot opponents. Combines powers with Kechizu for stronger effects.

data.name: Choso
data.appearance: Tall with red markings, wears modern clothing mixed with traditional elements.
data.personality: Protective of his brothers, calm but deadly in battle.

abilities.description: Controls his own blood for offense and defense. Skilled in close combat.

data.name: Ko-Guy
data.appearance: Grasshopper-like with elongated limbs for piercing attacks.

abilities.description: High-speed movement and powerful leg strikes.

data.name: Fly Heads
data.appearance: Small, fly-like spirits with human heads.

abilities.description: Summoned in large numbers to overwhelm weak targets.

data.name: Kechizu
data.appearance: Grotesque with multiple mouths and dripping blood.
data.personality: Immature, relies on Eso for guidance.

abilities.description: Uses decaying blood to infect enemies. Fights alongside Eso.

data.name: Finger Bearer
data.appearance: Large, grotesque spirit with Sukuna's finger embedded.

abilities.description: Overwhelming strength and regeneration from Sukuna's power.

data.name: Toji Fushiguro
data.appearance: Muscular with scars, wears a casual outfit and wields cursed tools.

abilities.description: Superhuman physical abilities due to zero cursed energy.

data.name: Ganesha
data.appearance: Elephant-headed deity curse.

abilities.description: Removes physical and metaphysical obstacles.
A high-ranking American military officer with unknown combat abilities.
A special grade curse that infects and entraps opponents using disease-based techniques.

data.name: Rika Orimoto
data.appearance: Shadowy figure with a monstrous form.

abilities.description: Grants immense cursed energy and weapons to Yuta.

data.name: Kurourushi
data.appearance: Cockroach-like with a grotesque humanoid shape.

abilities.description: Controls swarms of cockroaches and wields a cursed sword.

data.name: Kuchisake-Onna
data.appearance: Woman with a slit mouth, inspired by the urban legend.

abilities.description: Semi-grade 1 curse capable of using a simple domain.

data.name: Tamamo-no-Mae Incarnate
data.appearance: Mysterious humanoid curse with fox-like features.

abilities.description: Special grade curse with unconfirmed abilities.

data.name: Cyrus Veil
data.appearance: Government official in a formal suit.

abilities.description: High-ranking U.S. official involved in jujutsu affairs.

data.name: Keita Oe
data.appearance: Average-looking civilian with casual clothing.

abilities.description: No known jujutsu abilities.

data.name: Jin Itadori
data.appearance: Resembles Yuji; wears a lab coat.

abilities.description: Yuji's father; abilities unconfirmed.

data.name: Saori
data.appearance: Young woman with short hair and casual attire.

abilities.description: No confirmed jujutsu skills.

data.name: Takeda
data.appearance: Elderly man with glasses and a blue jumpsuit.

abilities.description: Unknown abilities.

data.name: Taichi Kanada
data.appearance: Blonde hair with a widow's peak; wears a red shirt.

abilities.description: No known jujutsu abilities.

data.name: Sotomura
data.appearance: Teenager with spiky hair and school uniform.

abilities.description: No known abilities.

data.name: Furudate
data.appearance: Old man with a twisted topknot and mustache.

abilities.description: Zenin clan elder; no combat abilities shown.

data.name: Tadashi Okazaki
data.appearance: Young student with short hair.

abilities.description: No known abilities.

data.name: Nagi Yoshino
data.appearance: Middle-aged woman with short hair.

abilities.description: Junpei's mother; no abilities.

data.name: Tsumiki Fushiguro
data.appearance: Young girl with short hair and gentle features.

abilities.description: No jujutsu abilities.

data.name: Shota Ito
data.appearance: Teenager with glasses and school uniform.

abilities.description: No abilities.

data.name: Takagi
data.appearance: Teenager with spiky hair.

abilities.description: No abilities.

data.name: Fumi
data.appearance: Young girl with long hair.

abilities.description: No abilities.

data.name: Nobuko Takada
data.appearance: Tall with twin tails and stylish clothing.

abilities.description: No jujutsu abilities.

data.name: Wasuke Itadori
data.appearance: Elderly man with wrinkles; resembles Yuji.

abilities.description: Yuji's grandfather; no abilities.

data.name: Yuko Ozawa
data.appearance: Blonde hair; wears a gray long-sleeved shirt.

abilities.description: No abilities.

data.name: Curse User
data.appearance: Generic curse user; varies.

abilities.description: Generic category of rogue jujutsu users.

data.name: Shigeru Sonoda
data.appearance: Elderly with a round indentation on his forehead.

abilities.description: No abilities.

data.name: Takeshi Iguchi
data.appearance: Teenager with short hair.

abilities.description: No abilities.

data.name: Setsuko Sasaki
data.appearance: Teenager with glasses and a bob cut.

abilities.description: No jujutsu abilities.

data.name: Shiu Kong
data.appearance: Middle-aged man with a suit.

abilities.description: No confirmed abilities.

data.name: Noritoshi Kamo (Ancestor)
data.appearance: Older man with a mustache and scarred forehead.

abilities.description: Infamous for experiments; mixed blood with Death Paintings.

data.name: Junpei Yoshino
data.appearance: Teenager with messy hair and a hoodie.

abilities.description: Summons a jellyfish-like shikigami.

data.name: Kokun
data.appearance: Wears a mask and cape; part of Q organization.

abilities.description: No confirmed abilities.

data.name: Ogami
data.appearance: Elderly woman with a bun and kimono.

abilities.description: Summons spirits into vessels (e.g., Toji).

data.name: Bayer
data.appearance: Long-haired with a mask; Q member.

abilities.description: Uses cursed daggers in combat.

data.name: Niji Ebina
data.appearance: Muscular with exposed gums and no eyelids.

abilities.description: No notable abilities.

data.name: Uraume
data.appearance: Androgynous with white hair and traditional robes.
data.personality: Loyal to Sukuna; calm and deadly.

abilities.description: Freezes targets with cursed energy.

data.name: Juzo Kumiya
data.appearance: Bald with dark markings; wears an apron.

abilities.description: Creates cursed tools like Haruta's sword.

data.name: Haruta Shigemo
data.appearance: Blonde ponytail with purple markings.

abilities.description: Survives fatal hits due to luck.

data.name: Jiro Awasaka
data.appearance: Elderly but muscular; wears a haramaki.

abilities.description: Reverses damage taken back to attackers.

data.name: Kenjaku
data.appearance: Uses Suguru Geto's body with an exposed brain on the forehead.
data.personality: Manipulative, intelligent, with long-term goals. Seeks to evolve humanity through cursed techniques.

abilities.description: Can transfer his brain to other bodies, inheriting their techniques. Master strategist.

data.name: Manami Suda
data.appearance: Young woman with long light hair, wears elegant dresses.
data.personality: Shares Geto's ideology. Loyal and devoted to his cause.

abilities.description: Skilled commander, exact abilities unclear.

data.name: Toshihisa Negi
data.appearance: Muscular with mid-length disheveled hair and a scar.
data.personality: Believes in Geto's vision. Pragmatic and focused.

abilities.description: Combat skills unknown but likely high-level.

data.name: Miguel
data.appearance: Tall African man with sunglasses and a large beret.

abilities.description: Skilled in hand-to-hand combat. Uses special cursed rope.

data.name: Mimiko Hasaba
data.appearance: Young girl with short black hair in a bob cut.
data.personality: Loyal to Geto, deeply attached to her sister Nanako.

abilities.description: Controls a cursed doll for attacks.

data.name: Nanako Hasaba
data.appearance: Long caramel hair tied in a bun, wears kogal-style outfits.
data.personality: More outspoken than Mimiko, equally devoted to Geto.

abilities.description: Fights alongside Mimiko with complementary techniques.

data.name: Larue
data.appearance: Large shirtless man with light hair and heart tattoos.
data.personality: Peacekeeper in Geto's group. Values family bonds.

abilities.description: Physical strength likely, exact abilities unknown.

data.name: Rika (Manifestation)
data.appearance: White skull-like head with black mass body and human arms.
data.personality: Obeys Yuta's commands but retains some autonomy.

abilities.description: Massive cursed energy reserves. Can act independently.

data.name: Dagon
data.appearance: Humanoid with octopus-like head and aquatic features.
data.personality: Initially timid, becomes aggressive after evolving.

abilities.description: Controls water and summons fish shikigami.

data.name: Ui Ui
data.appearance: Young boy with light blue hair in formal attire.
data.personality: Extremely devoted to his sister Mei Mei. Mature for his age.

abilities.description: Can teleport himself and others. Skilled assistant.

data.name: Rokujushi Miyo
data.appearance: Bald with spiky hair around the sides, wears only a sumo loincloth.
data.personality: Obsessed with sumo. Friendly despite battle circumstances.

abilities.description: Uses sumo wrestling moves in combat. Exceptional physical strength.

data.name: Hagane Daido
data.appearance: Elderly man with short grey hair and samurai attire.

abilities.description: Peerless sword skills despite no cursed energy.

data.name: Hanami
data.appearance: Humanoid with bark-like skin and flower features.
data.personality: Calmest of Disaster Curses. Values nature's balance.

abilities.description: Controls plants and absorbs energy from environment.

data.name: Jogo
data.appearance: Humanoid with volcanic rock skin and flaming head.
data.personality: Arrogant but recognizes true strength. Loyal to Sukuna.

abilities.description: Controls fire and lava.

data.name: Riko Amanai
data.appearance: Young girl with long dark hair in a braid.
data.personality: Feisty but kind. Values her newfound friendships.

abilities.description: Destined to merge with Tengen. No combat abilities.

data.name: Mahito
data.appearance: Patchwork skin with stitches, gray-blue hair, and heterochromatic eyes.
data.personality: Sadistic and playful. Believes he embodies human hatred.

abilities.description: Can reshape souls and bodies.

data.name: Misato Kuroi
data.appearance: Long black hair in a bun, wears a maid-like uniform.
data.personality: Kind and fiercely protective of Riko Amanai.

abilities.description: Skilled caretaker, no combat abilities.

data.name: Charles Bernard
data.appearance: French descent with steel-blue hair and eccentric clothing.
data.personality: Arrogant manga artist obsessed with his dreams.

abilities.description: Predicts enemy movements via drawings. Uses a cursed staff.

data.name: Dhruv Lakdawalla
data.appearance: Elderly Indian man with long hair and beard.

abilities.description: Summons lethal shikigami in circular patterns.

data.name: Remi
data.appearance: Attractive young woman with scorpion-tail hair.

abilities.description: Used as bait by Reggie Star. Abilities unclear.

data.name: Reggie Star
data.appearance: Light-haired with paper tags covering his torso.
data.personality: Playful but deadly. Values strong allies.

abilities.description: Creates objects from receipts. Skilled strategist.

data.name: Takako Uro
data.appearance: Pink hair, black sclera, wears minimal clothing.
data.personality: Proud and hot-tempered. Former Toh assassin.

abilities.description: Controls the sky as solid terrain.

data.name: Chizuru Hari
data.appearance: Muscular with a ponytail and cargo pants.

abilities.description: Never revealed his technique before death.

data.name: Ryu Ishigori
data.appearance: Tall with spiky hair and a scar over his eye.

abilities.description: Highest cursed energy output among players.

data.name: Iori Hazenoki
data.appearance: Long hair, wears suspenders without a shirt.
data.personality: Violent with a temper. Enjoys torture.

abilities.description: Detaches and explodes body parts (eyes/teeth).

data.name: Yorozu
data.appearance: Inhabits Tsumiki's body with dark hair and combat attire.
data.personality: Obsessed with Sukuna. Wild and brash.

abilities.description: Creates indestructible constructs. Domain: Unknown.

data.name: Rin Amai
data.appearance: Young with long light hair and a tracksuit.

abilities.description: No combat abilities. Used as pawn by Hanyu.

data.name: Hana Kurusu
data.appearance: Short light hair with a halo and angelic wings.

abilities.description: Nullifies cursed techniques. Shares body with Angel.

data.name: Hiromi Higuruma
data.appearance: Wears a judge's robe with tired eyes.
data.personality: Former lawyer. Fair but ruthless in trials.

abilities.description: Conducts trials that confiscate abilities or inflict death.

data.name: Fumihiko Takaba
data.appearance: Comedian with a microphone headset.
data.personality: Goofy but kind. Believes in his jokes.

abilities.description: Makes jokes reality. Power scales with his confidence.

data.name: Hajime Kashimo
data.appearance: Elderly with white hair and staff.

abilities.description: Generates and manipulates electricity. One-time use: suicide attack.

data.name: Hanyu
data.appearance: Muscular woman with aviator glasses.

abilities.description: Uses hair to fly and attack at high speed.

data.name: Haba
data.appearance: Short with propeller blades on his head.

abilities.description: Spinning blades can cut through steel.

data.name: Nobuaki Zenin
data.appearance: Pompadour hairstyle, formal light-colored costume.

abilities.description: Skilled swordsman, but no match for Maki.

data.name: Jinichi Zenin
data.appearance: Muscular with wild spiky hair and X-shaped scar.

abilities.description: Unleashes barrage of giant fists in combat.

data.name: Naobito Zenin
data.appearance: Gray hair with English-style mustache.

abilities.description: Fastest sorcerer after Gojo. Freezes targets in frames.

data.name: Ogi Zenin
data.appearance: Middle-aged with traditional Zenin attire.
data.personality: Abusive father to Maki and Mai.

abilities.description: Skilled in cursed tools, but inferior to Toji.

data.name: Ranta Zenin
data.appearance: Young with disheveled hair tied in a low ponytail.
data.personality: Devoted to clan. Willing to sacrifice himself.

abilities.description: Immobilizes targets with eye contact.

data.name: Chojuro Zenin
data.appearance: Old with a mohawk and grinning expression.

abilities.description: Summons giant stone hands to crush enemies.

data.name: Naoya Zenin
data.appearance: As human: slicked-back hair. As curse: worm-like with multiple eyes.
data.personality: Arrogant and misogynistic. Obsessed with speed.

abilities.description: Moves at Mach 3.

data.name: Sukuna
data.appearance: Currently in Megumi's body with black sea-urchin hair and tattoos.
data.personality: Sadistic and arrogant. Views humans as insects.

abilities.description: Slashes that adapt to target's toughness. Creates a fire arrow that can be shot

data.name: Momo Nishimiya
data.appearance: Short with blonde pigtails and witch-like outfit.
data.personality: Reserved but values female solidarity in jujutsu.

abilities.description: Flies on broom and marks targets for allies.

data.name: Noritoshi Kamo (Student)
data.appearance: Tall with wrapped strands of black hair (later cut short).
data.personality: Stoic but conflicted about clan politics.

abilities.description: Controls blood for projectiles and close combat.

data.name: Takuma Ino
data.appearance: Beanie hat with rolled-up ski mask. Lost an eye.
data.personality: Cheerful and looks up to Nanami.

abilities.description: Summons shikigami based on Chinese zodiac signs.

data.name: Tengen
data.appearance: Four-eyed cylinder head with robe (evolved beyond humanity).
data.personality: Detached but protective of jujutsu society.

abilities.description: Creates nationwide barriers. Merges with Star Plasma Vessels.

data.name: Yuki Tsukumo
data.appearance: Long blonde hair, sleeveless vest, baggy pants.
data.personality: Nonchalant but deeply ideological. Mentor to Todo.

abilities.description: Controls virtual mass for devastating attacks.

data.name: Mei Mei
data.appearance: Silver braided hair, dark bodysuit with skirt.
data.personality: Greedy but professional. Values money above all.

abilities.description: Controls crows for scouting and suicide attacks.

data.name: Aoi Todo
data.appearance: Muscular with top-knot and scarred face.
data.personality: Boisterous and obsessed with 'types' of women.

abilities.description: Swaps places with allies/cursed energy targets. Exceptional hand-to-hand combatant.

data.name: Yoshinobu Gakuganji
data.appearance: Elderly with a bald head, piercings, and traditional attire. Uses a cane.
data.personality: Traditionalist, scheming, and prioritizes student safety despite conflicts.

abilities.innate_technique: Uses a guitar to produce sound waves that can exorcise curses.
abilities.description: Can manipulate sound to attack or defend, with precise control over cursed energy.

data.name: Kasumi Miwa
data.appearance: Long light blue hair, wears a standard Jujutsu High uniform.
data.personality: Kind-hearted, hardworking, and self-deprecating. Fights to support her family.

abilities.description: Creates a 2.21-meter radius zone where she can instantly intercept attacks with her sword.

data.name: Yu Haibara
data.appearance: Short dark hair, wears a cropped Jujutsu High uniform.
data.personality: Optimistic and cheerful, proud to be a sorcerer.

abilities.description: Unknown abilities.

data.name: Arata Nitta
data.appearance: Unknown

abilities.description: Unknown abilities.

data.name: Suguru Geto
data.appearance: Long black hair tied up, wears monk attire.
data.personality: Hates non-sorcerers, condescending, but cares for fellow curse users.

abilities.special_trait: Can absorb and control cursed spirits.
abilities.innate_technique: Cursed Spirit Manipulation: Can collect and summon curses at will.
abilities.description: Can unleash multiple curses simultaneously and combine them for powerful attacks.

data.name: Kokichi Muta
data.appearance: Slim, with bandaged body and a top-knot.
data.personality: Reclusive, resentful of his condition, but determined.

abilities.special_trait: Can control multiple Mechamaru puppets remotely.
abilities.innate_technique: Puppet Manipulation: Uses cursed energy to pilot mechanized puppets.
abilities.description: Can unleash stored cursed energy for powerful attacks, including a special grade output mode.

data.name: Mai Zenin
data.appearance: Short black hair, resembles her twin Maki.
data.personality: Snarky, resentful of Maki, but ultimately self-sacrificing.

abilities.special_trait: Can create simple objects like bullets.
abilities.innate_technique: Construction: Limited to small, simple items due to low cursed energy.
abilities.description: Uses a revolver with cursed energy-infused bullets for precise long-range attacks.

data.name: Utahime Iori
data.appearance: Long blackish-purple hair, wears traditional miko attire with a facial scar.
data.personality: Calm and professional, but easily irritated by Gojo's antics.

abilities.innate_technique: Can enhance allies' cursed energy output through ritualistic singing.
abilities.description: Her technique temporarily boosts the power of other sorcerers' abilities when she performs.

data.name: Nobara Kugisaki
data.appearance: Orange hair with bangs, wears a gakuran-style uniform.

abilities.innate_technique: Straw Doll Technique: Can damage targets by hammering nails into effigies.
abilities.description: Her attacks affect both the physical body and the soul, making her effective against Mahito.

data.name: Kirara Hoshi
data.appearance: Feminine with long dark hair and star-shaped pupils.
data.personality: Loyal to Hakari, playful but protective.

abilities.innate_technique: Love Rendezvous: Marks objects to control their movement via constellation patterns.
abilities.description: Can manipulate marked objects to attract or repel based on the Southern Cross constellation alignment.

data.name: Kinji Hakari
data.appearance: Tall with a light purple afro, wears a fur coat.
data.personality: Charismatic gambler who thrives on risk.

abilities.innate_technique: Idle Death Gamble: Activates a pachinko-style domain for random power boosts.
abilities.description: When hitting a jackpot, gains 4 minutes and 11 seconds of infinite cursed energy and automatic regeneration.

data.name: Panda
data.appearance: Anthropomorphic panda, often wears accessories.
data.personality: Upbeat and sarcastic with a unique worldview.

abilities.innate_technique: Core Switching: Changes forms (Gorilla, Triceratops, Panda) with different abilities.
abilities.description: Each core provides unique combat abilities and enhanced durability.

data.name: Toge Inumaki
data.appearance: Spiky hair with snake-and-fang markings on cheeks and tongue.
data.personality: Quiet but deeply caring for allies.

abilities.innate_technique: Cursed Speech: Commands become reality but damage his throat.
abilities.description: Stronger commands cause more physical backlash (e.g., "Die" can rupture his vocal cords).

data.name: Kento Nanami
data.appearance: Blonde hair with glasses, wears a suit and tie.
data.personality: Rational and professional with a strong work ethic.

abilities.innate_technique: Ratio Technique: Creates weak points at 7:3 divisions of targets.
abilities.description: His blunt sword deals guaranteed critical hits when striking these predetermined points.

data.name: Yuta Okkotsu
data.appearance: Messy black hair, wears a modified Jujutsu High uniform.
data.personality: Initially timid but grows into a protective fighter.

abilities.special_trait: Massive cursed energy reserves. Rika manifestation
abilities.innate_technique: Copy.This ability allows him to replicate techniques he has observed or been exposed to, provided he meets certain conditions
abilities.description: Rika acts autonomously with immense strength and can copy others' techniques.

data.name: Maki Zenin
data.appearance: Short black hair, wears glasses (pre-Shibuya).
data.personality: Determined to prove herself outside clan politics.

abilities.innate_technique: None (Heavenly Restriction grants physical prowess at the cost of cursed energy).
abilities.description: Wields cursed tools expertly and perceives curses through special glasses.

data.name: Yuji Itadori
data.appearance: Spiky pink hair, athletic build, wears a hooded Jujutsu High uniform.
data.personality: Optimistic and values all lives, but struggles with Sukuna's influence.

abilities.special_trait: Enhanced physical capabilities. Shows a great capacity to use curse energy, like the Black Flash
abilities.innate_technique: None (inherited Sukuna's techniques, like cleave, later).
abilities.description: Excels in hand-to-hand combat and can temporarily host Sukuna's power.
abilities.domain_expansion: Unknown domain name, seems to be a copy of his hometown

data.name: Kiyotaka Ijichi
data.appearance: Black hair with glasses, wears a manager's suit.

abilities.innate_technique: Can erect simple curtains to conceal jujutsu activities.
abilities.description: His barriers are weaker than sorcerers' but effective for civilian protection.

data.name: Akari Nitta
data.appearance: Light-colored hair, wears a black suit.

abilities.innate_technique: Can slow bleeding and stabilize injuries using cursed energy.
abilities.description: Her technique prevents fatal blood loss but doesn't heal wounds completely.

data.name: Shoko Ieiri
data.appearance: Long brown hair, often tired-eyed, wears a lab coat.
data.personality: Laid-back but highly competent as a doctor.

abilities.innate_technique: Can heal others by reconstructing flesh with reversed cursed energy.
abilities.description: One of the few who can use RCT on others, making her invaluable for recovery.

data.name: Atsuya Kusakabe
data.appearance: Spiky brown hair, wears a peacoat over formal attire.

abilities.innate_technique: New Shadow Style: Batto Sword Drawing.
abilities.description: Specializes in anti-domain techniques and quick-draw sword attacks.

data.name: Megumi Fushiguro
data.appearance: Spiky black hair, wears a high-collared uniform.
data.personality: Serious and strategic, values efficiency in combat.

abilities.innate_technique: Ten Shadows Technique: Can summon 10 unique shikigami from shadows.
abilities.description: Shikigami gain new forms when exorcised (e.g., Divine Dogs → Totality).

data.name: Satoru Gojo
data.appearance: Tall with white hair and blindfold/glasses, wears a black uniform.
data.personality: Playful but deeply protective of students.

abilities.innate_technique: Limitless: Controls space at an atomic level (Infinity, Blue, Red, Purple).
abilities.description: His Six Eyes allow precise cursed energy control, making him nearly invulnerable.
